legacy.full_text: In a speech addressed to the #G20summit, #XiJinping expounded the Global Development Initiative (GDI) and the Global Security Initiative (GSI), offering China's vision of global governance as the world faces more complex challenges.

legacy.description: Commentator, Host of CGTN Radio/China Radio International. zhaoyingcri@foxmail.com
legacy.name: Zhao Ying

legacy.full_text: Biden's National Security Strategy says China is "the only competitor with both the intent to reshape the international order and, increasingly, the economic, diplomatic, military, and technological power to do it." These are misinterpretations of China's strategic intentions.

legacy.description: Commentator, Host of CGTN Radio/China Radio International. zhaoyingcri@foxmail.com
legacy.name: Zhao Ying

legacy.full_text: China has never attempted to reshape the international order, if the international order refers to the UN charter and the international law. What China is attempting to do is to improve the international order with more voices and input from the developing world.

legacy.description: Commentator, Host of CGTN Radio/China Radio International. zhaoyingcri@foxmail.com
legacy.name: Zhao Ying

legacy.full_text: The face-to-face meeting between #XiJinping and #JoeBiden is in itself a positive signal to the world. But the ball is in Washington's court to fix the bilateral relationship.

legacy.description: Commentator, Host of CGTN Radio/China Radio International. zhaoyingcri@foxmail.com
legacy.name: Zhao Ying

legacy.full_text: Despite all the new provocations from the US, China remains calm and sober and tries to avoid being drawn into the adversarial stance that the US has been trying to encourage.

legacy.description: Commentator, Host of CGTN Radio/China Radio International. zhaoyingcri@foxmail.com

legacy.full_text: President Xi said that he takes very seriously President Biden's statement of "five-noes". However, it remains to be seen whether Biden’s deeds will match his words.
